{"tid":1365510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因政見或其他原因係屋企唔開心既巴絲","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:16:08.000Z","uid":84793,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7731dd7089167fc0d318b54b12cc0ccd80fbffc","tid":1365510,"uid":84793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然屋企人唔認同自己想法係遺憾<br />\n但做人正正係要堅持自己認為食對的事<br />\n就算呢個世界全部人都唔支持都好<br />\n<br />\n更何況你仲有我地<br />\n我地雖然互不相識<br />\n但一齊發過同一個夢<br />\n而家可能好難捱<br />\n但痛苦總有一天會過去<br />\n黑暗過後就會見到曙光<br />\n我地要鬥長命<br />\n<br />\n覺得絕望不如係度傾下<br />\n或者留個tg開個group咁<br />\n你地並唔係自己一個<br />\n休息是為了走更遠既路"},{"pid":"0d1c0077dbfa5d37daa7ea27bc273d59825b2c42","tid":1365510,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"肥西老母雞湯"},{"pid":"57a5cc3d968920673fe898783dd9941addcf00ef","tid":1365510,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:12:45.000Z","msg":"肥雞老母劏閪"},{"pid":"0156c1f6a4c28b88166bbee950019db4e3f4d99b","tid":1365510,"uid":84793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb565f7bb373888502daf82df9768b0fc2e544e7","tid":1365510,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0156c1f6a4c28b88166bbee950019db4e3f4d99b","tid":1365510,"uid":84793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:17:11.000Z","msg":"鼓勵人用返個莊重啲個名"},{"pid":"9b6dabae3c5e7f6fffed4aa57546810c48f2451f","tid":1365510,"uid":84793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb565f7bb373888502daf82df9768b0fc2e544e7","tid":1365510,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0156c1f6a4c28b88166bbee950019db4e3f4d99b","tid":1365510,"u